metadata.name: Express Yourself - The FASHION Edition
metadata.description:
The FASHION Edition is 1 of a 3-part series called ‘Express Yourself’.

Each piece that makes up the series is hand drawn and professionally shot onto a 70 x 100 cm exhibition grade canvas.

Resolution: 6720 x 9600

All of the women who make up this collection are a symbolism of rebellion for those who want to affirm themselves with their needs, desires and dreams.
With the NFT, the original owner (first owner) has the right to redeem the physical artwork.
